Smart Planter IOT

Concept:
A smart planter box capable of managing a planterbox so that a plant can grow without supervision.
Data is viewed or box is controlled via an IoT interface.

Goals:
 * Box is able to record temperature.
 * Box is able to record moisture.
 * Box is able send data to a remote.
 * Box is reasonably insulated.

Hardware:
 * Raspberry Pi 3 B